snippet.textDisplay:
I ate Papa Johns last week (first time in over 5 years). It was disgusting. There was only one woman running the store at lunch time. I watched her answer the phones, prep pizzas and take cash. Their new garlic Romano crust is horrible- it's too salty and the cheese doesn't melt correctly and has a burnt terrible flavor. My pizza was trash. I will never go again. It appears that standards have fallen and their cut-backs at the franchise-level have adversely affected quality. They can hire all the black athletes they want to be their spokesman in order to prove to the world their company isn't racist but if the product is shit- their sales will be shit.
Their stock peaked 3 years ago. Memo to the board: Get Woke- Go Broke.
snippet.textOriginal:
I ate Papa Johns last week (first time in over 5 years).  It was disgusting.  There was only one woman running the store at lunch time. I watched her answer the phones, prep pizzas and take cash.  Their new garlic Romano crust is horrible- it's too salty and the cheese doesn't melt correctly and has a burnt terrible flavor.  My pizza was trash. I will never go again.  It appears that standards have fallen and their cut-backs at the franchise-level have adversely affected quality.  They can hire all the black athletes they want to be their spokesman in order to prove to the world their company isn't racist but if the product is shit- their sales will be shit. 
Their stock peaked 3 years ago.   Memo to the board: Get Woke- Go Broke.
